Putin recognized the DLNR. And before that, part of the residents of Donetsk and Luhansk, for no apparent reason, were forcibly taken to Russia as "refugees" in order to force Putin to recognize the independence of the DPR and LPR. Otherwise, he did not agree. Give me, he says, refugees, otherwise I won't recognize them. "Tell me, can we return home now?" forced refugees are now asking, having earned 10,000 rubles on this, “Or wait a little longer until Putin agrees to annex the LDNR to Russia? So that we don’t have to go back and forth twice.